'''''The University of Sanbra Guide to Intelligent Life''''' was a book on alien species written by [[Professor/Legends|Professor]] [[Tem Eliss]], of the [[University of Sanbra]]. Professor Eliss was forced to go into hiding from [[Commission for the Preservation of the New Order/Legends|COMPNOR]] when his book's pro-alien views were discovered by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] spies, and the first draft was anonymously leaked to underground communication networks.

==Behind the scenes==
The sourcebook ''[[Galaxy Guide 12: Aliens — Enemies and Allies]]'' was designed to be a collection of 'excerpts' from the first volume of ''The University of Sanbra Guide to Intelligent Life''.

A regular feature in ''[[Star Wars Gamer]]'' magazine was also titled [[The University of Sanbra Guide to Intelligent Life (Star Wars Gamer)|''The University of Sanbra Guide to Intelligent Life'']].

